Air Quality Monitors in 2015

The Chelan-Douglas-Okanogan area had 9 monitor-deployments during the 2015 July - October wildfire season. This includes both regulatory monitors that are part of the EPA AQS system as well as temporary monitors deployed by state and federal agencies during wildfires.
